* zahabu
* cassiterite (amabati)
* wolframite (ubutare bwa tungsten)
* columbite-tantalite (tantalum na niobium ore)
* methane
* amashanyarazi
* [[ikawa]]
* icyayi
* ubutaka bwo guhinga
* icyatsi kibisi

